Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}风学姐 姿势自然点就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只是下意识啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}话说你最近很热衷摄影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}学姐快要毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}留下部员们的活动纪录是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过我就算毕业 也会常来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还要待在这里啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我就猜到你会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嘴上这么说其实很高兴吧 夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你这是什么反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}看着她们就涌起我的创作欲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你也觉得吧 桑乔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这孩子能说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}风风学姐和小鱼干给我好多灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我回去就以她们为原型写本书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}再见 园园
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对了 毕业旅行去哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}年末的时候哪里都没去成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就是啊 用大赦的公费一起去泡温泉怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我之前去泡过温泉 能换个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}登山也很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}登山？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}迷路的小猫咪 你在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对了树 用猫语叫它出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喵～喵～喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}再…再野性一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真棒 寸寸真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:40.83,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}请不要拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}过来 一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈好眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我吓到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}寻找小猫的委托完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}学姐 拍一张照留作纪念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:14.63,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}その先でまた会えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:14.63,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}在漫长旅路的前方与你重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们唱得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}配合也完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们也来唱一首吧 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 等一下就写作业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}睡糊涂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小鱼干 我们一起唱个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}能聊一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}聊什么 夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}去走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好久没来这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}上次救东乡的时候来过而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我能先问个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抱歉 我都没考虑到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}换个地方吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}之前风说过 毕业后也会常来社团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我听她那么说或许有点开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有点？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是…也还是很…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:07:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你看 我也学会把心里话说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈也说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}年末这阵子 友奈你好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一定发生什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我会帮助你的 能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不管是什么烦恼 我都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我很在乎你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要是为了你 我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我好高兴 有个朋友能让我这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是友奈你们 让我有这份心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}发生什么事了 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真的…没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者部不是…「有烦恼要跟大家说」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我真的很想帮上朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛 等一下 夏凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈最近的样子果然不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是大吉耶 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不对 抽到大吉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈会笑得更灿烂才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但为何她的表情看上去这么难受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她肯定碰上什么不好跟我们说的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我来查明真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康宋体W5\bord0.3\blur7.5\shad4.5\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(480,907.5)}目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康宋体W5\bord0.3\blur7.5\shad4.5\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(720,907.5)}睡眠中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康宋体W5\bord0.3\blur7.5\shad4.5\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(1175,907.5)}可以入侵室内。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康宋体W5\bord0.3\blur7.5\shad4.5\3c&H120F07&\4c&H120F07&\pos(672,907.5)}收到。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康宋体W5\bord0.3\blur7.5\shad4.5\3c&H120F07&\4c&H120F07&\pos(980,907.5)}请原地待命。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康宋体W5\bord0.3\blur7.5\shad4.5\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(655,907.5)}开始入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康宋体W5\bord0.3\blur7.5\shad4.5\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(1150,907.5)}请打开锁。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康宋体W5\bord0.3\blur7.5\shad4.5\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(875,907.5)}收到。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈 灯都没关就睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抱歉 我偷偷进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈刚上中学时 4月3日托父母买却从未翻过的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这套丛书居然有一本凸了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者御记…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么里面藏着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可能…不对 这里面肯定有线索
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我就借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是友奈写的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈最近的样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}原因可能就写在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}居然还有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我能插句话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}园园？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也担心悠悠 就调查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我最近不是比大家早回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}其实是去大赦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大赦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我先说结论 悠悠的样子会不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}其实是因为受天神的神罚所苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}园园 你是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}听我说 鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}根据大赦的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果悠悠把神罚说出来 写下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神罚便会传染
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以这本日记是非常危险的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们还是要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}当然 我很担心友奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那一起来看悠悠的御记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}最开始是在年末
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大赦的人发觉我情况有异 专程上门来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他们通过神嘱和研究 已经查明了情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他们希望我能写日记 留下神圣的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}便给了我这本御记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我能坚持下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么会变这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:13:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我在大战中受到了巨大的消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}全身几乎散花殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我甚至因为触碰到了敌人的御魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}自己的灵魂也被御魂吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等我醒过来 那里是我救东乡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是一片辽阔无垠的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我奋力挣扎 想要逃出这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这里却是那么的宽广 走也走不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家 救救我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就算孤身一人 勇者也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:14:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者也不会放弃战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要信念还在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}希望就不会消散…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}无论有任何代价 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡 东乡 东乡！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我 不希望 失去最宝贵的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我 我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者不会对哭泣的朋友坐视不理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者就看毅力 我一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}蓝乌鸦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想蓝乌鸦是叫我跟它走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以我朝着光芒的方向不断前行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}于是我终于回到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但身体却不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我和大家从散花状态恢复了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但并非是献上的祭品回到了我们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}恢复的身体能力是神树大人创造的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}花了很多时间 才成了我们自己身体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了治愈强行满开 最后散花的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神树大人把我全身都变成了自己做的零件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大赦称我为「御姿」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「御姿」说好听点 是种非常神圣的存在
